♪ Ooh-eh♪

12:34.057 --> 12:36.146
-Oh-pah!

12:43.850 --> 12:45.852
-Zombra, zombra, zombra.

12:45.895 --> 12:48.028
Zambra, zombra.

12:48.071 --> 12:49.333
Why is he looking at his phone?

12:49.377 --> 12:51.118
It probably just can't wait.
It's an emergency.

12:51.161 --> 12:55.339
Z-Zombra, zambra,
zombra, zombra, zombra.

12:55.383 --> 12:58.038
Zombarisa...

12:58.081 --> 12:59.691
Hai! Hai! Hai!
Hai, hai, hai!

12:59.735 --> 13:01.171
Ba-boom!

13:02.607 --> 13:04.696
-Oh!
-Ew!
-Get in, you bastard!

13:04.740 --> 13:08.178
The end.
I have achieved reanimation.

13:08.222 --> 13:09.963
Your beloved familiar

13:10.006 --> 13:11.965
will return to you tomorrow.

13:12.008 --> 13:14.619
-Tomorrow?
-Life takes time, my friend.

13:14.663 --> 13:18.058
We are reversing the very powerof nature itself.

13:18.101 --> 13:20.060
But there's
a-a quickening ritual,

13:20.103 --> 13:21.931
if you want
to chivvy things along.

13:21.975 --> 13:24.107
As we're all friends,
I could do it for a hundy.

13:24.151 --> 13:26.109
-No, you bloody won't.
We're not interested.

13:26.153 --> 13:28.068
Thank you so very much, Wallace.

13:28.111 --> 13:29.547
♪ Zappidee-doo.♪

13:29.591 --> 13:31.811
Zappidee-doo.

13:37.164 --> 13:39.122
Everything is back to normal,
because our Topher is back!

13:39.166 --> 13:40.645
It's true.
I've got to admit,

13:40.689 --> 13:42.952
Wallace, as contemptible
a man as he is,

13:42.996 --> 13:47.087
-actually came up trumps.
-: Told you so.

13:47.130 --> 13:50.220
You fucking didn't.

13:50.264 --> 13:53.093
Don't tell Guillermo, but...

13:53.136 --> 13:55.399
I'm so happy Topher is back.

13:56.792 --> 13:59.621
All right,
let us begin with the minutes.

13:59.664 --> 14:01.231
I am here.

14:01.275 --> 14:03.451
Guillermo, you are there.

14:03.494 --> 14:05.105
And, um...

14:05.148 --> 14:06.889
TOPHER :
To-pher!

14:06.933 --> 14:08.369
NADJA :
Oh, Tophie!

14:08.412 --> 14:09.457
And there is Topher.

14:09.500 --> 14:10.588
Wonderful.

14:10.632 --> 14:12.286
We are all here.
We can begin.

14:12.329 --> 14:14.201
Firstly--
and I'm not naming names--

14:14.244 --> 14:17.291
but I have recently noticed
that the house reeks

14:17.334 --> 14:20.076
of decaying flesh, and there aredead birds everywhere.

14:20.120 --> 14:21.686
TOPHER:
Topher!

14:21.730 --> 14:23.514
As I say, I'm not naming names.

14:23.558 --> 14:25.473
But if we do have an issue,

14:25.516 --> 14:27.475
then it's important
that we all work together

14:27.518 --> 14:30.304
to let Guillermo know,
so that he can fix it.

14:30.347 --> 14:32.262
TOPHER:
Doze Apples!

14:35.526 --> 14:36.788
LASZLO:
Off he goes.

14:36.832 --> 14:38.529
That chap's tireless, isn't he?

14:38.573 --> 14:41.576
You could learn something
from Topher, no, Guillermo?

14:41.619 --> 14:43.491
