I'm good at reading and writing.

23:43.596 --> 23:46.468
Yes, you are. You know,
I wanted to be a writer
when I was a kid.

23:46.512 --> 23:48.557
Or an artist, you know?

23:48.601 --> 23:50.646
Cartoonist, maybe.
Combine the two.

23:50.690 --> 23:51.691
Why didn't you?

23:53.519 --> 23:55.216
-Wake up!

23:55.259 --> 23:56.913
-You two came along.

23:56.957 --> 23:58.698
-Bing, bing, bing!
-Oh!

23:58.741 --> 24:00.656
-Life gets in the way, don't it?--

24:01.265 --> 24:02.484
Oh. Ow!

24:02.528 --> 24:03.703
You drift.

24:03.746 --> 24:05.052
-Ahh.

24:05.095 --> 24:07.489
I'm not blaming you.
