I would like to explore the idea

24:14.931 --> 24:16.585
of tokenism
in the workplace,

24:16.629 --> 24:19.109
where one minority is propped up

24:19.153 --> 24:21.677
to cover the experience
of the entire population.

24:21.721 --> 24:23.244
WOMAN: That's interesting.

24:23.287 --> 24:25.289
Wait. Sorry. You're not sayingyou feel that way here?

24:34.429 --> 24:37.040
